<hr />

<p><br /></p>

<p>Inputs are used when user data is required. It can be a text, a number, booleans, dates, etc. Using an informative <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">placeholder</code> is preferrable.</p>

<h2 id="basic-text">Basic text</h2>
<p>For single line inputs.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<div class="flex flex-col w-1/2">
    <label for="first-name">First Name</label>
    <input type="text" id="first-name" class="mt-2" placeholder="Write your first name here" />
</div>

<p><br /></p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"flex flex-col w-1/2"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;label</span> <span class="na">for=</span><span class="s">"first-name"</span> <span class="nt">&gt;</span>First Name<span class="nt">&lt;/label&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"first-name"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"mt-2"</span> <span class="na">placeholder=</span><span class="s">"Write your first name here"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

<h2 id="text-area">Text area</h2>
<p>For multiline inputs.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<div class="flex flex-col">
    <label for="message">Biography</label>
    <textarea id="message" class="mt-2"></textarea>
</div>

<p><br /></p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"flex flex-col"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;label</span> <span class="na">for=</span><span class="s">"biography"</span> <span class="nt">&gt;</span>Biography<span class="nt">&lt;/label&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;textarea</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"biography"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"mt-2"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

